show.title: The World in my grasp

show.description: Finn Cooper works hard as a laborer, saving every penny to marry his girlfriend. One day, he wishes to be stronger—and suddenly, everyone else becomes as weak as water. Now the strongest man on Earth, Finn faces a world that’s nothing like he imagined.
